<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>守望网络期刊第22期 on 北京守望教会</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%8A%E7%AC%AC22%E6%9C%9F/</link><description>Recent content in 守望网络期刊第22期 on 北京守望教会</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:46:03 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://shwchurch3.github.io/categories/%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E6%9C%9F%E5%88%8A%E7%AC%AC22%E6%9C%9F/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>简讯</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E7%AE%80%E8%AE%AF-17/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:46:03 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E7%AE%80%E8%AE%AF-17/</guid><description>3月4日，本主日共有7位弟兄姊妹因户外敬拜被扣留。截止到当天晚上7点多时，所有弟兄姊妹均被释放。详情请见《北京守望教会2012年3月4日户外</description></item><item><title>基督徒生命的见证/天明牧师</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E5%BE%92%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%81%E5%A4%A9%E6%98%8E%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%88/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:31:31 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%9F%BA%E7%9D%A3%E5%BE%92%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%81%E5%A4%A9%E6%98%8E%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%88/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;……蒙神伟大救恩而拥有天上荣耀、活泼盼望的基督徒，作为“客旅”在地上“寄居”的期间，……，“要禁戒（与灵魂争战的）肉体的私欲”、“应当品行端正”，有这样的“好行为”，才能在毁谤基督徒的外邦世界及外邦人中至终成为荣耀神的见证。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>蒙神喜悦的生命/袁灵传道</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E8%92%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%96%9C%E6%82%A6%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E8%A2%81%E7%81%B5%E4%BC%A0%E9%81%93/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:30:30 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E8%92%99%E7%A5%9E%E5%96%9C%E6%82%A6%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E8%A2%81%E7%81%B5%E4%BC%A0%E9%81%93/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;敬虔的生命不是表现在轰轰烈烈的事件中，而是表现在平平常常的生活中；圣洁的样式也不在于我们是什么叱咤风云、举足轻重的人物，而是体现在我们作为国民、作为老板或员工、作为丈夫或妻子、作为父母或儿女这些基本角色中。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>我的产业，坐落在佳美之处/HY</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E5%9D%90%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%B3%E7%BE%8E%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%84hy/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:17:43 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%A7%E4%B8%9A%E5%9D%90%E8%90%BD%E5%9C%A8%E4%BD%B3%E7%BE%8E%E4%B9%8B%E5%A4%84hy/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我又一次经历了神的恩典，因每次他们说时都有一句话在我心里涌出：主用绳量给我的地界，坐落在佳美之处。是的，我的产业实在是美好。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>病中絮语（一）：一波三折、有惊无险的“死亡”之旅/午炎</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E7%97%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%B5%AE%E8%AF%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%89%E6%8A%98%E6%9C%89%E6%83%8A%E6%97%A0%E9%99%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:04:40 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E7%97%85%E4%B8%AD%E7%B5%AE%E8%AF%AD%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%80%E6%B3%A2%E4%B8%89%E6%8A%98%E6%9C%89%E6%83%8A%E6%97%A0%E9%99%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;医生、药物都不可靠，病人自己更不可靠，我们能不能存活，全仰赖上帝自己。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>和的哥谈福音（3）/铁皮娃娃</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%92%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%93%A5%E8%B0%88%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B33%E9%93%81%E7%9A%AE%E5%A8%83%E5%A8%83/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:03:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%92%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%93%A5%E8%B0%88%E7%A6%8F%E9%9F%B33%E9%93%81%E7%9A%AE%E5%A8%83%E5%A8%83/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;要是有一天，大街小巷上跑的出租车都播放着赞美诗，的哥成了流动的宣教士，那多好啊。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>家书（五）/ 曾淼</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%A6%E4%BA%94-%E6%9B%BE%E6%B7%BC/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:03:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%AE%B6%E4%B9%A6%E4%BA%94-%E6%9B%BE%E6%B7%BC/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;就是在孤独中，依然能够从神那里感受到他的爱、并且获得爱的能力，从而在重压下心灵里面依然有空间接纳他人、承载他人。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>蒙恩的确据/孙毅长老</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E8%92%99%E6%81%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E6%8D%AE%E5%AD%99%E6%AF%85%E9%95%BF%E8%80%81/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:02:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E8%92%99%E6%81%A9%E7%9A%84%E7%A1%AE%E6%8D%AE%E5%AD%99%E6%AF%85%E9%95%BF%E8%80%81/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;这确据是从上赐下来的，人一旦得到，就成为生命中最为确定的磐石。确定到它超越人的思想意识，甚至让人思想意识中不时流露出来的怀疑根本就达不到它。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>神的沉默/金子</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E9%87%91%E5%AD%90/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:02:10 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E9%BB%98%E9%87%91%E5%AD%90/</guid><description>&lt;p align=&#34;left&#34;&gt;
若建堂并现在的户外是因着神对教会的信任而发出沉默时，我们则更要在他面前安静并生发对他的敬畏！
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>读书随想：读《神的杰作》有感/WN</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3%E8%AF%BB%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%B0%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%9Fwn/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 08:01:37 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E9%9A%8F%E6%83%B3%E8%AF%BB%E7%A5%9E%E7%9A%84%E6%9D%B0%E4%BD%9C%E6%9C%89%E6%84%9Fwn/</guid><description>&lt;p align=&#34;left&#34;&gt;
从普世教会的角度来看，基督是教会的头，众教会彼此互为肢体，或者说是身体上的细胞，都听从惟一身体领导的指挥。
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>根/HJ</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%A0%B9hj/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:57:54 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%A0%B9hj/</guid><description>&lt;p align=&#34;left&#34;&gt;
我想上帝乃是要将他自己根植于我们生命当中去，也是因为冲击太大所以就要扎根更深。因此，我们若是被上帝连根拔起，就要感恩！
&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>十字架——给儿子讲解属灵原则的实际应用/阿淘妈妈</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E6%9E%B6-%E7%BB%99%E5%84%BF%E5%AD%90%E8%AE%B2%E8%A7%A3%E5%B1%9E%E7%81%B5%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E9%98%BF%E6%B7%98%E5%A6%88/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:57:19 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E6%9E%B6-%E7%BB%99%E5%84%BF%E5%AD%90%E8%AE%B2%E8%A7%A3%E5%B1%9E%E7%81%B5%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%99%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9E%E9%99%85%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8%E9%98%BF%E6%B7%98%E5%A6%88/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;考虑到他的理解能力，平日唯恐他所信的不过是父母的遗传，不愿意使用字句灌输只当做教训和大道理告诉他，却没有带出属灵的实际，今日想换个他能理解的方式。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>妙语摘录 / XF等</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%A6%99%E8%AF%AD%E6%91%98%E5%BD%95-xf%E7%AD%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:56:33 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%A6%99%E8%AF%AD%E6%91%98%E5%BD%95-xf%E7%AD%89/</guid><description>守望小方：守望教会的信徒被剥夺买卖权，被搬家，被失业，被堵锁眼，被非法限制人身自由1年，被遣返原籍，被禁止吃饭，被非法继续盘问，被满口谎言，</description></item><item><title>怎么能摆脱对于娱乐的沉迷/约翰•派博</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E8%83%BD%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E7%BA%A6%E7%BF%B0%E6%B4%BE%E5%8D%9A/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:55:27 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E8%83%BD%E6%91%86%E8%84%B1%E5%AF%B9%E4%BA%8E%E5%A8%B1%E4%B9%90%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%89%E8%BF%B7%E7%BA%A6%E7%BF%B0%E6%B4%BE%E5%8D%9A/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我很深的为此担忧。我想持守关于神的严肃，而不是通过把他变得有乐趣，来让他变得更“可口”。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>教理问答连载之三</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%95%99%E7%90%86%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%E8%BF%9E%E8%BD%BD%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%89/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:54:43 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E6%95%99%E7%90%86%E9%97%AE%E7%AD%94%E8%BF%9E%E8%BD%BD%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%89/</guid><description>我们的情形看上去毫无希望：圣洁的神不能放过罪；有罪的人无能偿债；人以外也无受造者能够帮助。这就引起了一个几乎绝望的问题：那么我们必须寻找一位</description></item><item><title>北京守望教会3月4日户外敬拜通报</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A3%E6%9C%884%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%95%AC%E6%8B%9C%E9%80%9A%E6%8A%A5/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:53:50 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A3%E6%9C%884%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%95%AC%E6%8B%9C%E9%80%9A%E6%8A%A5/</guid><description>各位亲爱的弟兄姊妹： &amp;nbsp; 主内平安！本主日是今年的第十个主日，像过去的那些主日一样，在这三月份的第一周，弟兄姊妹继续在信心和盼望中来敬拜寻求我们</description></item><item><title>北京守望教会3月11日户外敬拜通报</title><link>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A3%E6%9C%8811%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%95%AC%E6%8B%9C%E9%80%9A%E6%8A%A5/</link><pubDate>Wed, 14 Mar 2012 07:53:09 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://shwchurch3.github.io/2012/03/14/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%88%E6%9C%9B%E6%95%99%E4%BC%9A3%E6%9C%8811%E6%97%A5%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E6%95%AC%E6%8B%9C%E9%80%9A%E6%8A%A5/</guid><description>&lt;hr /&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>